flowchart TD
    A[Start] --> B[Validate inputs]
    B --> C[Detect IronPython/Python2 features]
    C --> D{engine == auto?}
    D -- Yes --> E{Likely IronPython/Py2?}
    E -- Yes --> F[resolved_engine = ironpython2]
    E -- No --> G[resolved_engine = cpython3]
    D -- No --> H[resolved_engine = requested engine]

    F --> I[Normalize text]
    G --> I
    H --> I

    I --> J{Text empty after cleanup?}
    J -- Yes --> K[Return empty script and report]
    J -- No --> L[Dedent and normalize indentation]

    L --> M{auto_fix?}
    M -- No --> N[Join lines]
    M -- Yes --> O[Run fix passes up to max_passes]

    O --> P[General fixes]
    P --> Q{Resolved engine}
    Q -- cpython3 --> R[Modernize syntax and builtins]
    Q -- ironpython3 --> S[Modernize syntax, preserve clr/System]
    Q -- ironpython2 --> T[Preserve Python2 style mostly]
    Q -- ironpython --> U[Conservative IronPython preservation]

    R --> V[Re-normalize indentation]
    S --> V
    T --> V
    U --> V

    V --> W{Any changes?}
    W -- Yes --> O
    W -- No --> N

    N --> X{validate_python?}
    X -- No --> Y[Return script, fixes, report]
    X -- Yes --> Z{resolved_engine == ironpython2?}
    Z -- Yes --> AA[Validate modernized preview with ast.parse]
    Z -- No --> AB[Validate final script with ast.parse]

    AA --> AC{Valid?}
    AB --> AC
    AC -- No --> AD[Raise ScriptFormatError]
    AC -- Yes --> Y